Package curam.util.tab.impl

Contains the interfaces required for dynamic support of the tabbed user interface menu bar and navigation tree

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DynamicMenuStateLoader
    This class supports determining the state of menu items given a menu bar identifier, a list of menu item identifiers, and the list of loaders associated with a menu bar.
    DynamicNavStateLoader
    This class supports determining the state of navigation items given a navigation identifier, a list of navigation item identifiers, and the list of loaders associated with a tab navigation.
    MenuState
    Interface for the menu state cache.
    NavigationState
    Interface for the navigation state cache.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MenuStateFactory
    Factory class to return a menu state implementation that can be used for testing the dynamic menu state loaders.
    NavigationStateFactory
    Factory class to return a navigation state implementation that can be used for testing the dynamic navigation state loaders.

Package curam.util.tab.impl Description

Contains the interfaces required for dynamic support of the tabbed user interface menu bar and navigation tree.
Since:
Curam SDEJ6.0
